metadata.notes:
Purpose: The Unaami Data Collection is an interdisciplinary, diverse collection of Arctic variables which represent different geographic regions and data types. It includes basic physical meteorological and oceanographic data and "impact data" such as fisheries, marine mammals, ozone and plant changes.

Status: Complete

Maintenance frequency: Continually
